"title": "1080: God, living and self-sustaining",
"media_type": "Text",
"index_reference": "1080",
"language": "eng",
"review_level": "None",
"content": "<p>God is alive and active. In contrast to idols, he is uncreated and the source of all continuing life.</p>\n<h2>God is alive</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:10\">JER 10:10</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen1:1\">GEN 1:1</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut5:26\">DEU 5:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Josh3:10\">JOS 3:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer23:36\">JER 23:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt26:63\">MAT 26:63</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim3:15\">1TI 3:15</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12\">HEB 3:12</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb12:22\">HEB 12:22</a></p>\n<h2>God lives for ever</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa57:15\">ISA 57:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan4:34\">DAN 4:34</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan12:7\">DAN 12:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev4:9-Rev4:10\">REV 4:9–4:10</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev10:6\">REV 10:6</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rev15:7\">REV 15:7</a></p>\n<h2>God is self-existent</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:26\">JHN 5:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Exod3:14\">EXO 3:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John8:58\">JHN 8:58</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:25\">ACT 17:25</a></p>\n<h2>The living God is Father, Son and Holy Spirit</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John6:57\">JHN 6:57</a></strong>; <strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor3:3\">2CO 3:3</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Matt16:16\">MAT 16:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Cor8:6\">1CO 8:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb7:24\">HEB 7:24</a></p>\n<h2>The living God is to be worshipped</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:26\">DAN 6:26</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Dan6:20\">DAN 6:20</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Rom9:26\">ROM 9:26</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Hos1:10\">HOS 1:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Cor6:16\">2CO 6:16</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Tim4:10\">1TI 4:10</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb9:14\">HEB 9:14</a></p>\n<h2>Turning away from the living God is sin</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb3:12\">HEB 3:12</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:26\">1SA 17:26</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Sam17:36\">1SA 17:36</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:4\">2KI 19:4</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:4\">ISA 37:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/2Kgs19:16\">2KI 19:16</a> parallel <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa37:17\">ISA 37:17</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb10:31\">HEB 10:31</a></p>\n<h2>The living God contrasts with dead idols</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts14:15\">ACT 14:15</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Kgs18:26-1Kgs18:29\">1KI 18:26–18:29</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps115:2-Ps115:7\">PSA 115:2–115:7</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:1-Isa46:4\">ISA 46:1–46:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Jer10:3-Jer10:6\">JER 10:3–10:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Thess1:9\">1TH 1:9</a></p>\n<h2>God is the source of life</h2>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Deut30:20\">DEU 30:20</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John1:4\">JHN 1:4</a></p>\n<h3>God gives life to created beings</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Gen2:7\">GEN 2:7</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Job27:3\">JOB 27:3</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps104:30\">PSA 104:30</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa40:28\">ISA 40:28</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:25\">ACT 17:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Acts17:28\">ACT 17:28</a></p>\n<h3>God sustains the life of all people</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps54:4\">PSA 54:4</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Chr29:14\">1CH 29:14</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps3:5\">PSA 3:5</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps18:35\">PSA 18:35</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps146:9\">PSA 146:9</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps147:6\">PSA 147:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Isa46:4\">ISA 46:4</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Heb1:3\">HEB 1:3</a></p>\n<h3>God gives spiritual life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/John10:28\">JHN 10:28</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John5:21\">JHN 5:21</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John11:25\">JHN 11:25</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John14:6\">JHN 14:6</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/1Pet1:23\">1PE 1:23</a></p>\n<h3>God is the source of new life</h3>\n<p><strong><a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps42:2\">PSA 42:2</a></strong> <em>See also</em> <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps63:1\">PSA 63:1</a>, <a href=\"https://ref.ly/Ps84:2\">PSA 84:2</a>; <a href=\"https://ref.ly/John3:1-John3:8\">JHN 3:1–3:8</a></p>",
